<L>__{exterior an ornamental garden vienna afternoon 1780's}
<A>__{an outdoor concert is being given. mozart is actually playing the final movement of his e flat concerto with an orchestra. listening to him is a sizable audience, including the emperor, flanked by strack and von swieten. the crowd is in a happy and appreciative mood: it is a delightful open air scene. we hear the gayest and most complex passage. leopold and constanze listen to mozart, who plays his own work brilliantly. we stay with this scene for a little while and then}
